                "invention-title": [
                    "Marine wind power generation system",
                    "一种船用风力发电系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The marine wind power generation system comprises a stacked wind power generation device and a hydrogen production and storage device, and the stacked wind power generation device is composed of a rotating platform and a stacked fan frame provided with a power generation fan and can rotate around a rotating shaft connected with an upper building so as to flexibly adjust the state of the rotating platform under different wind speed conditions. And meanwhile, the hydraulic jacking device is used for jacking four corner points of the stacked fan frame at different heights, so that a proper included angle is formed between the stacked fan frame and the inlet air, and a proper attack angle of the blade is obtained to achieve the optimal blade tip speed ratio so as to ensure the maximum capture rate of wind energy. According to the wind power generation system, redundant electric energy can be converted into hydrogen energy with lower storage cost and transportation cost for storage through the hydrogen production equipment and the high-pressure gaseous hydrogen storage equipment, and the cost problem is solved. In general, the system can effectively promote low-carbon green operation of the ship."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种船用风力发电系统，包括叠式风力发电装置和制氢储氢装置，叠式风力发电装置由旋转平台和装有发电风机的叠式风机架组成，并能够绕与上层建筑连接的转轴转动，以在不同的风速条件下灵活调整旋转平台的状态。同时，通过液压顶升装置对叠式风机架四个角点进行不同高度的顶升，使叠式风机架与入流风之间形成合适的夹角，从而获得叶片的合适攻角以达到最佳叶尖速比，来保证风能最大捕获率。该风力发电系统通过制氢设备和高压气态储氢设备也能将冗余的电能转化为存储成本、运输成本更低的氢能进行存储，解决了成本问题。总体而言，该系统能够有效地推进船舶低碳绿色运营。"
                }
            ]
